(316, 'tivibu-ev-aile-paketi', 'Tivibu Ev Aile Paketi', '<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.32; margin-top: 8pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">TV keyfi avantajlı fiyatlarla her zaman, her yerde sizle!</span></h4><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 19pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tivibu’da ailece TV keyfini Aile Paketinde yaşayın !</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tivibu Ev veya Uydu teknolojisine göre sunulan farklı seçenekler ile Discovery, National Geographic ve History Channel gibi en kaliteli belgesel kanallarına TV, bilgisayar, tablet ya da cep telefonunuzdan kolayca ulaşın.</span></p></li><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">50’den fazlası HD* 130’a varan TV kanalı</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">*3500’ün üzerinde \"Seç İzle\" içeriği seçeneğiyle</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Ulusal, belgesel, çocuk, müzik, yaşam-eğlence</span></p></li></ul></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\">&nbsp;</p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a54deefc-7fff-b5a5-de0d-94ccf299801e\"><br></span></p>', '', '', 3, 'Tv', 'tv', 'Tivibu', 'tivibu', '19', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '24 Ay', 'Tivibu Ev Aile Paketi', 'Tivibu Ev Aile Paketi', 0, 1, 0, '2018-12-05 23:14:29'),
(317, 'tivibu-ev-sinema-paketi', 'Tivibu Ev Sinema Paketi', '<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.32; margin-top: 8pt; margin-bottom: 8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">TV keyfi avantajlı fiyatlarla her zaman, her yerde sizle!</span></h4><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sinema tutkunları ve dizi-belgesel severler için ne varsa Sinema Paketi’nde!</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Tivibu Ev veya Uydu teknolojisine göre sunulan farklı seçenekler ile Sinetivi, Sinetivi Adrenalin ve Sinetivi Karnaval kanallarında 7/24 film izleyin; Fox Life, FX, Fox Crime gibi dünyanın en popüler dizi kanallarındaki dizileri Amerika yayını ile aynı anda veya hemen sonra takip edin; Discovery, National Geographic ve BBC gibi en kaliteli belgesel kanallarına TV, bilgisayar, tablet ya da cep telefonunuzdan kolayca ulaşın.</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">“Uydu” başlığı altında, Tivibu Mod’unda yer alan kanalları bulabilirsiniz. Paket üyeliğiniz ile, bu kanallara ek olarak, Türksat üzerinden yayın yapan diğer uydu kanallarını da izleyebilirsiniz.</span></p></li><ul style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">30’dan fazlası HD* 190’a varan TV kanalı</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: circle; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">**4000’in üzerinde \"Seç İz